  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p class="updated">Last Updated: May 19, 2026</p>

</div>

</header>

<section class="privacy-content">

<div class="container">



<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>1.1 Automatically Collected Information</h3>

<p>When you visit DogeKing.us, we automatically collect certain information through Google Analytics 4 (GA4), including:</p>

<ul>

  <li>Device information (browser type, operating system, screen resolution)</li>

  <li>Usage data (pages visited, time spent, clicks, scroll depth)</li>

  <li>Referral information (how you found our site)</li>

  <li>Approximate geographic location (city/country level only)</li>

</ul>



<h3>1.2 Wallet Information</h3>

<p>If you connect your Solana wallet (Phantom, Solflare, Backpack), we collect your public wallet address. This is used solely for:</p>

<ul>

  <li>Displaying your wallet connection status</li>

  <li>Enabling referral tracking and rewards</li>

  <li>Verifying $DKING token holder status</li>

</ul>

<p>We never store your private keys or seed phrases. Wallet connection is handled entirely client-side.</p>



<h3>1.3 Email Information</h3>

<p>If you subscribe to our newsletter or purchase products, we collect your email address via Kit (ConvertKit). We use this only for sending requested updates and product delivery.</p>



<h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>

<ul>

  <li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>

  <li>Analyze traffic patterns and content effectiveness</li>

  <li>Process product orders through Gumroad</li>

  <li>Send newsletter updates (only with consent)</li>

  <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>

</ul>



<h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>

<p>We share data only with essential service providers:</p>

<ul>

  <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> - Website analytics (opt-out available via cookie consent)</li>

  <li><strong>Gumroad</strong> - Product sales processing</li>

  <li><strong>Kit (ConvertKit)</strong> - Email newsletter delivery</li>

  <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> - CDN and website hosting</li>

</ul>

<p>We never sell your personal data to third parties.</p>



<h2>4. Cookie Policy</h2>

<p>We use cookies for analytics and site functionality. You can control cookie preferences through our cookie consent banner. Essential cookies cannot be disabled as they are required for site operation.</p>



<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>

<p>We retain analytics data for 26 months (Google Analytics standard). Email subscription data is retained until you unsubscribe. Wallet connection data is not stored server-side.</p>



<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>

<p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>

<ul>

  <li>Access your personal data</li>

  <li>Request data deletion</li>

  <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>

  <li>Unsubscribe from marketing emails</li>

</ul>

<p>To exercise these rights, contact us via Telegram: @DogeKingArmy</p>



<h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>

<p>Our site contains links to third-party services (Gumroad, Solscan, DexTools, Jupiter, Telegram, X, Discord). These services have their own privacy policies, and we are not responsible for their practices.</p>



<h2>8. Security</h2>

<p>We implement industry-standard security measures including SSL/TLS encryption, Cloudflare DDoS protection, and secure API practices. However, no online service is 100% secure.</p>



<h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>Our services are not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>



<h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>We may update this policy periodically. Significant changes will be announced via our Telegram channel and website notice.</p>



<h2>11. Contact</h2>

<p>For privacy-related inquiries:<br>

Telegram: <a href="https://t.me/DogeKingArmy">@DogeKingArmy</a><br>

X/Twitter: <a href="https://x.com/dogekingcoin">@dogekingcoin</a></p>



